#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.18"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.18:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.18:0.2"
msgid "2. Vihāravagga"
msgstr "2. Meditation"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.18:0.3"
msgid "18. Paṭhamakukkuṭārāmasutta"
msgstr "18. At the Chicken Monastery (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.18:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "sn45.18:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ca ānando āyasmā ca bhaddo pāṭaliputte viharanti "
"kukkuṭārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the venerables Ānanda and Bhadda were staying at Pāṭaliputta, in "
"the Chicken Monastery."

msgctxt "sn45.18:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā bhaddo sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yenāyasmā ānando "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā ānandena saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then in the late afternoon, Venerable Bhadda came out of retreat, went to "
"Venerable Ānanda, and exchanged greetings with him."

msgctxt "sn45.18:1.4"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho āyasmā bhaddo āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side and said to Ānanda:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.16"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.18:2.1"
msgid "“‘Abrahmacariyaṃ, abrahmacariyan’ti, āvuso ānanda, vuccati."
msgstr "“Reverend, they speak of this thing called ‘not the spiritual path’."

msgctxt "sn45.18:2.2"
msgid "Katamaṃ nu kho, āvuso, abrahmacariyan”ti?"
msgstr "What is not the spiritual path?”"

msgctxt "sn45.18:2.3"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, āvuso bhadda."
msgstr "“Good, good, Reverend Bhadda!"

msgctxt "sn45.18:2.4"
msgid ""
"Bhaddako kho te, āvuso bhadda, ummaṅgo, bhaddakaṃ paṭibhānaṃ, kalyāṇī "
"paripucchā."
msgstr "Your approach and articulation are excellent, and it’s a good question."

msgctxt "sn45.18:2.5"
msgid "Evañhi tvaṃ, āvuso bhadda, pucchasi:"
msgstr "For you asked:"

msgctxt "sn45.18:2.6"
msgid "‘abrahmacariyaṃ, abrahmacariyanti, āvuso ānanda, vuccati."
msgstr "‘They speak of this thing called “not the spiritual path”."

msgctxt "sn45.18:2.7"
msgid "Katamaṃ nu kho, āvuso, abrahmacariyan’”ti?"
msgstr "What is not the spiritual path?’”"

msgctxt "sn45.18:2.8"
msgid "“Evamāvuso”ti."
msgstr "“Yes, reverend.”"

msgctxt "sn45.18:2.9"
msgid ""
"“Ayameva kho, āvuso, aṭṭhaṅgiko micchāmaggo abrahmacariyaṃ, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"“What is not the spiritual path is simply the wrong eightfold path, that is:"

msgctxt "sn45.18:2.10"
msgid "micchādiṭṭhi … pe … micchāsamādhī”ti."
msgstr ""
"wrong view, wrong thought, wrong speech, wrong action, wrong livelihood, "
"wrong effort, wrong mindfulness, and wrong immersion.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.18:2.11"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
